"       </td>",
"       <td>",
"        <a href=\"file://www.qualitymeasures.ahrq.gov/content.aspx?id=35534\" target=\"_blank\">",
"         file://www.qualitymeasures.ahrq.gov/content.aspx?id=35534",
"        </a>",
"       </td>",
"       <td>",
"        The measure is not based on any clinical guidelines, but a systematic literature review supports the measure",
"        <sup>",
"         [4]",
"        </sup>",
"       </td>",
"      </tr>",
"      <tr>",
"       <td>",
